# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OCGT Website — .gitignore
# Purpose: keep the repo lean + safe for team collaboration.
# GitHub limits: 100 MB/file hard, 1 GB/repo soft, 5 GB/repo hard.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── OS / editor artifacts ──────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.Spotlight-V100
.Trashes
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ── IDE / editor config (local-only) ───────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-*
*.code-workspace
.claude/
.history/

# ── Dependencies / build output ────────────────────────
node_modules/
dist/
build/
.next/
.cache/
.parcel-cache/
.vercel/
.netlify/

# ── Env / secrets ──────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
secrets.json
credentials.json
.aws/
.npmrc

# ── Logs ───────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
logs/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# OCGT-specific — DO NOT commit heavy assets to GitHub
# These live on the Strato upload only, or on shared cloud storage.
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Raw point-cloud / scan data (3+ GB single files)
*.las
*.laz
*.e57
*.ply
*.splat
*.npy
*.xyz
*.pcd
*.pts

# Design-tool source files
*.psd
*.ai
*.sketch
*.fig
*.xd
*.afdesign
*.afphoto

# Proprietary photo-processing sidecars
*.gsr2
*.cr2
*.nef
*.arw
*.dng

# ── Unused video masters (keep only what the site references) ──
# The live site uses: 04 Videos/Hero-web-compact.mp4 + .webm + hero-poster.jpg
04 Videos/*.mov
04 Videos/220915-final_h264*
04 Videos/260209-*
04 Videos/Hero.webm
04 Videos/Hero-web.mp4
04 Videos/Hero-web.webm
04 Videos/Sum/
04 Videos/Video 1/

# ── Marketing video masters (not referenced in live HTML) ──
marketing/*.mp4
marketing/*.mov

# ── Uncompressed raw images (10-33 MB each) — use WebP in build ──
# Only web-optimized images should live in git.
# Raw masters belong on shared drive.
Images/20*.jpg
Images/Bild*.JPG
Images/Bild*.jpg
Images/Hero.jpg
Images/Berlin Pro.jpg*
Images/Modell ETH.jpg*
Images/Quedlin*.jpg*
Images/Speyer.jpg*

