!Images/LOGO_black.png
!Images/LOGO website.png
!Images/LOGO website mit.png
!Images/LOGO NEU FINAL Logo2 .png
!Images/Hero.webp
!Images/DSO_A3 oRand.jpg
!Images/DSO_A3 oRand.webp
!Images/DSO_A3 oRand.avif
!Images/dronestep1.jpg
!Images/Speyer2.jpg
!Images/CUV_20170124_102444_mix01.jpg
!Images/20140213-140212_Trog 3_BT A_Vereisung-8_oRand.jpg
# Hero & sector card images referenced by OCGT_website.html:
!Images/Hero.jpg
!Images/Modell ETH.jpg
!Images/Quedlin.jpg
!Images/20180129_101219_stitch.jpg
!Images/20180327_101759.jpg
